##Female workers described the epidemic 02: the first daughter of the New Year fever, repeated fever, I was scared to death

Micro-signal kidsdoit

Function introduction, practice school (Beijing Xixi Children Care Center Vocational Training Department) , is a 15-18-year-old migrant children full-time, non-academic vocational education public welfare projects. The mission and vision are: to explore new career development paths for the children of migrant workers, and to cultivate "precious ordinary people" for a good society.

Editor = = = = = = = = = = = = 

Starting in 2019, the practical school for the children of migrant workers, and the Magnolia Flower for female workers, jointly organized a writing class for female workers, some of whom are domestic workers, some of whom are cooks, some of whom are salesmen.

Recently, we have some in Beijing, some in the home, more or less, have also been affected by the new pneumonia epidemic. We asked if we could write about our experiences during this time. As a result, we received quite a few articles.

Starting today, we're going to start sending out. You are welcome to read it, and you are welcome to give tips to the author. Your encouragement is very important. Thank you!

The Mulan Sisters'record under the outbreak

By Zhang Jingyun

Self Introduction: I am a domestic worker, junior high school graduates to work in Beijing, have done a lot of work, the longest job is domestic service.

☟

A few days before the New Year, the sisters are still busy doing Nougat, all of a sudden cold down, all go home reunion. A little lost.

He and his son planned to go to the movies this year, climb the Great Wall, go to temple fairs, and Climb Fragrance Hill. I haven't climbed Fragrance Hill in years, or twice before I was married.

On January 23, I went to Aobei market to buy some vegetables and meat. I didn't say that the epidemic was serious. I just said that the infection in Wuhan was very serious. I saw it on the news and didn't attach importance to it. I have an appointment with my uncle to play Mahjong.

On January 24, they started saying all kinds of things. They said that Wuhan was closed and the masks were sold out. Others said that a mask cost more than 10 yuan each. They only heard about it, but they didn't pass it around either. I saw 15 yuan two packs in a drugstore, which is the ordinary kind of masks.

January 24 noon, we eat, my daughter Liu Chen inadvertently said a mouth, "I may be sick" , I also scolded her, "nonsense, full of stuffed, what is not good, sick. ". And my sister said to be careful not to catch a cold. After lunch in the afternoon, we'll go to the worm's house to play Mahjong. They're watching TV.

Zhang Jingyun and her daughter Liu Chen

On the first afternoon of the Lunar New Year's Day on January 25, we went to play Mahjong. Our daughter was still lying on the bed with her legs crossed. Her uncle also said that she was just as comfortable as you are in bed. Nobody cares about her, and in the evening she says to me, "mom, I have a fever. ". My heart skipped a beat. My heart was in my throat. In this special period of fever, feeling not very good, I quickly give her a temperature of 38 degrees, how can this do?

We have an adult's fever medicine, not a child's. She has no cold symptoms, no runny nose, no cough, just a sore throat. No one had a cold all winter, no cold medicine, just Isatis Tinctoria. Took an adult fever medicine, cut it in half. One night also did not sleep much, have been watching her fever, every two or three hours to take a temperature, took the fever medicine to reduce the fever, medicine strength of a fever came up. What medicine also has at home, it is special period again, how to do?

The fever keeps coming back. I'm a little scared. The next day I took her to the drugstore to see if it was open. But there's only one dealer in there, and the owner's not here. Ask only to know, plus wechat video guide to buy medicine, bought a hundred dollars of medicine.

After buying medicine, I went to the street for a turn. The supermarket was not open. No one was in the street. Walking past the village committee, I saw my uncle's vegetable shop was open. Before I heard my sister said four uncle back home, to ask a vegetable shop to know, the epidemic is serious, he was afraid not to return to Beijing did not return.

In their vegetable shop chat for a while, also did not pay attention to the food will be so expensive, is that the new year prices rose a little high, who knows someone buy cabbage, said Cabbage 4 yuan per catty! ！! I don't know. Cabbage costs $4 a kilo. Shiji Jiafu supermarket owner also went over to chat, said he came to his hometown on the morning of New Year's Eve, immediately returned in the afternoon, the children did not bring back to Beijing.

Bought medicine to eat, Liu Chen or repeated fever, fever to 41 degrees. No, let's go to the hospital. Quarantine is quarantine. We can't keep running a fever like this. She was also afraid, said to drink a fever medicine, fever can not go to the hospital, and drink a fever medicine. I also gave her with white wine physical cooling, behind the ears, before and after the neck, armpits, before heart back back, inner thighs are wiped all over. Especially the back are wiped out measles, scarlet, and later become purple. By the middle of the night, her fever had finally subsided. The tonsil inflammation has not gone down, bought the medicine to eat up, also had to buy the medicine.

I went to the pharmacy again to buy medicine, did not open, to the drugstore owner message, he explained to me in Wechat "buy medicine" , he gave me a temporary password, and then scan the Qr code to enter the temporary password, the door lock will open.

Liu Chen had a fever on the night of the 25th of January, and it didn't subside until the 4th of the 28th of January. I was scared to death.

January 27, the third day of the Lunar New Year did not get up, the landlord gave us to ID cards account this office pass, no pass can only enter. I just got my I.D. , and I need a license and a license plate, and I need a license for my car.

And the landlord keeps telling me not to bring my husband back. They won't let me go home. They'll be quarantined for 14 days. Been following the news, a few outbreaks here, a few outbreaks there. The number of cases in Wuhan has increased from several thousand to more than 20,000. People are really in a state of trepidation. They do not know when the epidemic will pass. This year's people are in a state of fear.

Zhang Jingyun's recent circle of friends
